    "Case Study: the robot PERI.",
    "meets \"Clouded\" Meta-Forms",
    "Our second case study revolves around a very interesting and challenging reasoning game that we are using in a sustained attempt to quite literally have the cognitive robot PERI.2 attend school and progress grade-by-grade through at least high school, on the road thereby to artificial general intelligence (AGI); this project was announced in Bringsjord et al. (2022a).",
    "The game is called \"Meta-Forms\" (see Figure 2 for a rapid orientation to the game).",
    "For our second case study, PERI.2 is issued the challenge of solving a Meta-Forms problem; not one of the very hardest of such problems, but certainly a non-trivial one, even for adult humans; the problem is shown in Figure 3."
